## What it handles correctly

| Edge Case | Example | Result |
|---|---|---|
| Commas inside quotes | `"Smith, John"` | Single field |
| Escaped quotes `""` | `"Jane ""The Great"""` | `Jane "The Great"` |
| Multiline fields | `"line1\nline2"` | Preserved newline |
| Mixed quoted/unquoted | `Alice,35,"SF, CA"` | All 3 fields correct |
| Trailing newlines | Ends with `\n` | No phantom empty row |

