|---|---|
| **RFC 4180 parser** | Character-by-character state machine — correctly handles `""` escaped quotes, quoted fields with commas, and all three line endings (`\r\n`, `\n`, `\r`) |
| **Varying column counts** | Finds the maximum column count across all rows and pads shorter rows with empty cells |
| **Styled table** | Dark sticky header, alternating blue-tinted / white rows, hover highlight, clear 1 px borders |
| **Row numbers** | A muted `#` column lets you track position at a glance |
| **Empty-cell indicator** | Empty fields show `(empty)` in light grey italic so they're never invisible |
| **Header toggle** | Checkbox to treat the first row as a header or as data — re-parses live |
| **Status messages** | Green success / red error feedback beneath the controls |
| **Stats footer** | Shows row count, column count, and header mode below the table |
| **Keyboard shortcut** | `Ctrl+Enter` (or `Cmd+Enter`) triggers parsing |
| **Responsive** | Horizontally scrollable table wrapper; tightened padding on small screens |

