    <div class="section-title">⚠️ Why Regex Cannot Fully Validate Emails</div>

    <ul class="limitation-list">
      <li>
        <span class="bullet">📜</span>
        <span>
          <strong>RFC 5321 &amp; 5322 are enormous.</strong> The full specification
