        <span class="status-chip s-2xx">201 Created — new user created</span>
        <span class="status-chip s-4xx">400 Bad Request — invalid/missing fields</span>
        <span class="status-chip s-4xx">409 Conflict — email already exists</span>
        <span class="status-chip s-4xx">422 Unprocessable Entity — validation error</span>
      </div>
    </div>
