      <ul>
        <li>Never put sensitive data in query strings</li>
        <li>Always use HTTPS in production</li>
        <li>Use Authorization headers for tokens</li>
        <li>Validate and sanitize all inputs</li>
        <li>Rate-limit write endpoints</li>
        <li>Require explicit scoping for bulk ops</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="ref-card">
      <h4>📦 Request / Response Patterns</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Return <code>Location</code> header on 201</li>
        <li>Use JSON consistently (<code>Content-Type</code>)</li>
        <li>Wrap collections: <code>{"data":[], "meta":{}}</code></li>
        <li>Include pagination metadata</li>
        <li>Use consistent error object shape</li>
        <li>Support <code>If-Match</code> for optimistic locking</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="ref-card">
      <h4>🔢 Versioning Strategies</h4>
