**12 total issues caught across the four endpoints:**

| # | Endpoint | Key Problems |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | `GET /getUsers` | Verb in URL, singular name |
| 2 | `POST /user/delete/5` | Wrong HTTP method, verb in path, singular resource |
| 3 | `GET /createUser?name=Jo` | GET used for mutation, sensitive data in URL, verb in path |
| 4 | `PUT /updateAllUsers` | Verb in URL, wrong method for partial update, dangerous implicit bulk scope |

