### Key issues flagged across all 4 endpoints
1. **`GET /getUsers`** → verb in URL, missing plural, no pagination
2. **`POST /user/delete/5`** → wrong method, verb in URL, singular resource, broken idempotency
3. **`GET /createUser?name=Jo`** → GET for mutation, sensitive data in query string, verb in URL, no validation
4. **`PUT /updateAllUsers`** → PUT semantics misapplied to a collection, verb in URL, dangerous bulk op with no ID

