        </div>
        <p class="panel-desc">
            A <code>taskQueue</code> promise chain serializes all updates. Each task awaits
            its turn before reading and writing. A <code>clamp</code> guard also ensures
            the total never exceeds 100%, even if task increments are slightly too large.
        </p>

        <div class="progress-section" id="fixedTasks">
            <!-- Tasks injected by JS -->
        </div>

        <div class="total-section">
            <div class="total-label">Combined Progress (clamped to ≤ 100%)</div>
            <div class="total-value" id="fixedTotal">0%</div>
        </div>

        <div class="status-text">
            <span class="status-indicator idle" id="fixedIndicator"></span>
            <span id="fixedStatus">Ready to run</span>
        </div>

        <div class="log-box" id="fixedLog">
            <div class="log-entry info">// Fixed log will appear here...</div>
