<h1>⚡ Shared Mutable State & Concurrency</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Why naive progress tracking breaks — and exactly how to fix it</p>

<div class="panels">

  <!-- ══════════════════ BUGGY PANEL ══════════════════ -->
  <div class="panel buggy">
    <div class="panel-title">
