<h1>⚠ SHARED STATE CONCURRENCY BUGS</h1>
<p class="subtitle">setTimeout async tasks racing on shared mutable state — buggy vs fixed, side by side</p>

<div class="panels">

  <!-- ============================================================ BUGGY PANEL -->
  <div class="panel buggy" id="buggyPanel">
    <h2>💀 BUGGY VERSION <span class="status-badge badge-idle" id="buggyBadge">IDLE</span></h2>
    <p class="tagline">Multiple async tasks write shared progress without coordination</p>

